Definition: the people in a society considered as a system organized by a characteristic pattern of relationships
Example: the social organization of England and America is very different; sociologists have studied the changing structure of the family
Synonyms: social_organisation, social_structure, social_system, structure, system, society, m, the, people, in, a, considered, as, organized, by, characteristic, pattern, of, relationships, social, organization, England, and, America, is, very, different, sociologists, have, studied, changing, family
Category: noun.group
